Trade/Device Name(s): VALIDATE GC1 Calibration Verification / Linearity Test Set
VALIDATE GC2 Calibration Verification / Linearity Test Set
VALIDATE GC3 Calibration Verification / Linearity Test Set
VALIDATE GC4 Calibration Verification / Linearity Test Set
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for VALIDATE GC Calibration Verification / Linearity Test Sets for use in chemistry systems to assess calibration, reportable range, and linearity.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for in vitro diagnostic use in the quantitative determination of linearity, calibration verification and verification of reportable range in automated, semi automated, and manual chemistry systems.
